text: William Duncan Schuette ( ; born October 13, 1953) is an American politician and lawyer. He was the 53rd Attorney General of Michigan.AG-elect Bill Schuette announces transition team - Chicago Tribune, November 5, 2010 He was the Republican nominee for Governor of Michigan in the 2018 gubernatorial election losing to Gretchen Whitmer. ==References== ==Other websites== *Bill Schuette for Michigan Attorney General *Office of the Attorney General *Project Vote Smart – Bill Schuette profile *Our Campaigns – Bill Schuette profile * Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Michigan attorneys general Category:People from Midland, Michigan Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
